name: FootnoteFirstBaseline
shortdesc: Options for specifying the amount of vertical space between the top of the footnote container and the first line of footnote text.

property.name: ASCENT_OFFSET
property.shortdesc: The tallest character in the font falls below the top of the footnote container.

property.name: CAP_HEIGHT
property.shortdesc: The tops of upper case letters touch the top of the footnote container.

property.name: LEADING_OFFSET
property.shortdesc: The leading value of the text defines the distance between the baseline of the text and the top of the footnote container.

property.name: EMBOX_HEIGHT
property.shortdesc: The em box height of the text defines the distance between the baseline of the text and the top of the footnote container.

property.name: X_HEIGHT
property.shortdesc: The tops of lower case letters without ascents, such as x, touch the top of the footnote container.

property.name: FIXED_HEIGHT
property.shortdesc: The footnote minimum first baseline offset value defines the distance between the baseline of the text and the top of the footnote container.
